   at Avl.TestAutomationFramework.Infrastructure.UnitTests.TestDriver.Base.TestFixtureSetUp() in D:\git\TestAutomationFramework_V2013\Projects\Infrastructure\UnitTests\TestDriver\Base.cs:line 13
